name: M³Space
description:
M³Space DAO is an organization focused on investing in NFT assets such as MeatVerse digital lands, investing in ongoing contributions to the development of the MetaVerse.
Each M³ Space DAO member has a unique community interest-based NFT and access to a LOOT-based DID on-chain identity NFT that is programmable and scalable, with a changing NFT appearance as the user's contributions to the DAO community such as voting, governance, and donations grow, and the value of each user's on-chain identity continues to accumulate and appreciate.
